OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fincreasingly bright end to the
OL,7,Fafternoon, with sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping this evening. Plenty of
OL,9,Fclear periods are expected overnight,
OL,10,Fparticularly in the east. It will be a
OL,11,Fwarm and humid night, with
OL,12,Ftemperatures remaining in double
OL,13,Ffigures.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,16,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. A small
OL,17,Fchance of a few light showers later in
OL,18,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,19,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
